 printing for years: cheaper, faster, and often times higher quality. There=
 are, to be certain, companies and startups using 3D printing to that end (=
notably, SpaceX) but the promise of ubiquitous 3D printing still seems some=
what far off.</p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: =
